(1, 1, 'Nova Noir', 49.99, 'Eau De Parfum 100ml | Unisex', 'Inspired by the mysteries of the night sky, this opulent fragrance blends sweet apple, warm cinnamon, and alluring tonka.', 'Nova Noir, an opulent and sophisticated fragrance that captivates the senses with its unparalleled luxury. Inspired by the mysteries of the night sky, Nova Noir embodies the enchanting allure of a starlit evening. Opening with a burst of tantalizing apple, zesty lemon, and warm cinnamon, this velvety scent evokes an aura of refinement. Lavender and bergamot add a touch of freshness, while fruity accords infuse the fragrance with vibrancy. At its heart, tonka and jasmine create a luscious and inviting aroma, complemented by the earthy notes of oak and green accords. As the fragrance settles, a rich base of praline, vanilla, and sandalwood envelops the senses, leaving a trail of warmth and sensuality. With hints of amber, musk, and patchouli, Nova Noir lingers on the skin, leaving an unforgettable impression.', 'NOVA-NOIR-67a3504ea2088.png', 'Nova-Noir-02-672093e819630.jpg', 'Nova-Noir-05-672093e819a50.jpg', 'Nova-Noir-03-672093e819e2d.jpg', 'Nova-Noir-01-672093e81a281.jpg', NULL, 'Oriental Woody', 'Nova-Noir-Family-JPG-Destop-04-671b6d58b8603.jpg', 'Nova-Noir-Family-JPG-Destop-04-671b6e503ec4d.png', NULL, 'A Starlit Symphony', 'Nova-Noir-Top-Note-JPG-Destop-03-671b6d58b8ab5.jpg', 'Nova-Noir-Top-Note-PNG-Mobile-03-min-671b6e503f13c.png', NULL, 'Fresh Floral Opulence', 'Nova-Noir-Middle-Note-JPG-Destop-02-671b6d58b8dfe.jpg', 'Nova-Noir-Middle-Note-PNG-Mobile-02-min-671b6e503f4d4.png', NULL, 'Warm Sensuality', 'Nova-Noir-Base-Note-JPG-Destop-01-671b6d58b905b.jpg', 'Nova-Noir-Base-Note-PNG-Mobile-01-min-671b6e503f86e.png', 'nova-noir', '1', '2024-07-29 05:42:36', '2025-04-25 11:40:19', 'Opulent, Sophisticated, Velvety', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'NOVA-NOIR-674ff0d2e2007.png', 'NOVA-NOIR-6763af2cbbc0b.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Evening | Night', 'Vegan &<br>Cruelty-free', 'Contains<br>Natural Oils', 'Contains<br>Essential Oils', NULL, 'Copaiba Balsam Oil, Eugenol, Italian Finest Lemon Oil, Labdanum Resinoid, Bergamot Oil.', NULL, 'Oriental Woody', 'Nova-Noir-67162bffb43ec.png', 'Orange Oil, Sage Clary Oil, Myrrh Oil, Patchouli Oil.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Unveil the Mystery of Nova Noir, Bold Elegance by Maison de l\'Avenir', 'Discover the captivating aroma of Nova Noir, a sophisticated unisex fragrance from Maison de l\'Avenir\'s exclusive range of luxury fragrances.', 'Nova Noir', 'According to our AI, rich amber draws 78% of U.S. buyers who value long-lasting scents.*', 'https://a.co/d/bLYz366', 'https://www.allbeauty.com/maison-de-lavenir-elixir-collection-nova-noir-eau-de-parfum-spray-100ml/15789705.html', '4'),
(2, 1, 'Oud Intense', 49.99, 'Eau De Parfum 100ml | Unisex', 'Discover the essence of Middle Eastern fragrance rituals with exquisite Boya Oud essential oil blended with Rose absolute.', 'Oud Intense, where the essence of Middle Eastern fragrance rituals awaits, provoking memories of intimate gatherings suffused with the exotic scent of oud and delicate florals. At its heart, Oud Intense embodies the spirit of these cherished traditions, intertwining velvety magnolia, leather oud, and Cambodian oud into a fragrance that evokes a sense of luxury and tradition. With each application, Oud Intense envelops you in its rich embrace, leaving an indelible reminder of the timeless allure of Middle Eastern perfumery and the captivating power of scent.', 'OUD-INTENSE-6703c264e6dba.png', 'Oud-Intense-02-6728628e64d48.jpg', 'Oud-Intense-05-6728628e6528f.jpg', 'Oud-Intense-03-6728628e656ca.jpg', 'Oud-Intense-01-6728628e65ede.jpg', NULL, 'Floral Oriental', 'Oud-Intense-Family-JPG-Destop-4-671b7028775c7.jpg', 'Oud-Intense-Family-PNG-Mobile-04-min-671b70287883a.png', NULL, 'A Citrus Burst<br>of Freshness', 'Oud-Intense-Top-Note-JPG-Destop-3-671b70287792e.jpg', 'Oud-Intense-Top-Note-PNG-Mobile-03-min-671b702878b75.png', NULL, 'Fresh Floral<br>Opulence', 'Oud-Intense-Middle-Note-JPG-Destop-2-671b702877b33.jpg', 'Oud-Intense-Middle-Note-PNG-Mobile-02-min-671b702878e1f.png', NULL, 'Intricate Layers<br>of Aromas', 'Oud-Intense-Base-Note-JPG-Destop-1-671b702878211.jpg', 'Oud-Intense-Base-Note-PNG-Mobile-01-min-671b702879127.png', 'oud-intense', '1', '2024-07-30 10:14:16', '2025-04-25 11:18:34', 'Intense, Oriental, Hypnotic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'OUD-INTENSE-674ff121a8df3.png', 'OUD-INTENSE-676ac1d6368c8.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Evening | Night', 'Cruelty-free', 'Contains<br>Natural Oils', 'Contains<br>Essential Oils', NULL, 'West Australian Sandalwood Oil, Patchouli Oil, Copaiba Balsam Oil, Eugenol, Ylang Ylang Oil.', NULL, 'Floral Oriental', 'Oud-Intense-6717357912f76.png', 'Boya Oud, Russ