(11, 3, 'Midnight Solstice', 39.99, NULL, 'Inspired by moonlit dunes and starlit skies,  the fragrance blends velvety magnolia, leather oud, amber and Cambodian oud.', 'As the night unfolds in the Arabian desert, Midnight Solstice emerges with an aura of majesty, capturing the essence of moonlit dunes and starlit skies. Opening with pink pepper and saffron, it evokes the vibrant energy of Arabian nights, while bergamot and raspberry offer a fruity freshness. The heart reveals opulent magnolia and leather oud, blending seamlessly with blond wood. Base notes of Cambodian oud, patchouli, and vetiver evoke rugged landscapes, while suede, labdanum, and amber add sophistication.', 'Midnight-Solstice-6703f738aff02.png', 'Midnight-Solstice-02-67345abccce9e.jpg', 'Midnight-Solstice-05-67345abccd293.jpg', 'Midnight-Solstice-03-67345abccd5d7.jpg', 'Midnight-Solstice-01-67345abccd982.jpg', NULL, 'Oriental Woody', 'Midnight-Solstice-Family-JPG-Destop-04-671b768b715d9.jpg', 'Midnight-Solstice-Family-PNG-Mobile-0-671b768b71ef0.png', NULL, 'A Nocturnal Beauty with a Mystical Promise', 'Midnight-Solstice-Top-Note-JPG-Destop-03-671b768b718bb.jpg', 'Midnight-Solstice-Top-Note-PNG-Mobile-0-671b768b7218e.png', NULL, 'Exotic Nights in Leathered Luxury', 'Midnight-Solstice-Middle-Note-JPG-Destop-02-671b768b71aef.jpg', 'Midnight-Solstice-Middle-Note-PNG-Mob-671b768b72442.png', NULL, 'Deep Aromas of Soulful Treasures', 'Midnight-Solstice-Base-Note-JPG-Destop-01-671b768b71cf6.jpg', 'Midnight-Solstice-Base-Note-PNG-Mobi-671b768b7273f.png', 'midnight-solstice', '1', '2024-07-30 15:36:19', '2024-12-24 14:23:00', 'Arabian, Majestic,  Sophisticated', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'MIDNIGHT-SOLSTICE-674ff21b7fd99.png', 'MIDNIGHT-SOLSTICE-676ac3c42fbe8.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Evening/Night/Special Occasions', 'Vegan &<br>Cruelty-free', 'Contains<br>Natural Oils', 'Contains<br>Essential Oils', NULL, 'Patchouli Oil, Vetiver, Elemi, Egyptian Geranium Oil, Bergamot Oil.', NULL, 'Oriental Woody', 'Midnight-Solstic