(12, 2, 'Oud Opulence', 39.99, 'Eau De Parfum 100ml | Unisex', 'Experience the grandeur and sophistication of Ara bian culture, as this fragrance intertwines saffron, oud, and leather in a majestic blend.', 'Drawing inspiration from the grandeur and sophistication of Arabian culture, Oud Opulence captures the essence of luxurious refinement. The fragrance opens with an exquisite blend of saffron, caramel, and bergamot, setting the stage for a journey of unparalleled elegance. The heart of Oud Opulence reveals the timeless beauty of rose, oud, and cedarwood, combining to create a warm, woody essence. Luxurious accords of leather, patchouli, and geranium add depth and complexity, embodying the intricate artistry and tradition of Arabian heritage. As the fragrance settles, base notes of moss, vetiver, vanilla, and musk evoke the timeless elegance of the Arabian landscape. Amber and sandalwood add a touch of sensuous warmth.', 'Oud-Opulence-6703e60b477db.png', 'Oud-Opulence-03-6765837998596.jpg', 'Oud-Opulence-02-6765837998bd4.jpg', 'Oud-Opulence-05-6765837998f2e.jpg', 'Oud-Opulence-01-6734594d1c406.jpg', NULL, 'Oriental', 'Oud-Opulence-Family-JPG-Destop-04-671b72ec39f49.jpg', 'Oud-Opulence-Family-PNG-Mobile-04-min-671b72ec3ae31.png', NULL, 'A harmony of rich warmth <br>and floral freshness', 'Oud-Opulence-Top-Note-JPG-Destop-03-671b72ec3a3ae.jpg', 'Oud-Opulence-Top-Note-PNG-Mobile-03-min-671b72ec3b0ab.png', NULL, 'Fresh and woody <br>aromas at the heart', 'Oud-Opulence-Middle-Note-JPG-Destop-02-671b72ec3a718.jpg', 'Oud-Opulence-Middle-Note-PNG-Mobile-02--671b72ec3b32d.png', NULL, 'A serenade of spices <br>and warm woods', 'Oud-Opulence-Base-Note-JPG-Destop-01-671b72ec3aa7e.jpg', 'Oud-Opulence-Base-Note-PNG-Mobile-01-m-671b72ec3b5ad.png', 'oud-opulence', '1', '2024-07-30 15:44:24', '2025-04-25 11:19:02', 'Refined, Timeless, Regal', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'OUD-OPULENCE-674ff23141ac3.png', 'OUD-OPULENCE-676ac5a34b502.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Evening/Night', 'Cruelty-free', 'Co