(13, 2, 'Avenir Triumph', 39.99, 'Eau De Parfum 100ml | Unisex', 'An olfactory testament to the human spirit,  this scent bursts with mandarin orange and bergamot, woven with cinnamon and leather.', 'Avenir Triumph, an olfactory testament to the indomitable human spirit, draws from the wellspring of triumphs that define our journey. Inspired by the euphoric crescendo of accomplishment, this fragrance is a tapestry of vibrant citrus, warm spices, and grounding woody accords. The invigorating burst of mandarin orange and bergamot, woven with cinnamon and ginger, unfurls into a base of amber and leather, resonating with the enduring fortitude of the triumphant soul.', 'Avenir-Triumph-6703e56c250c3.png', 'Avenir-Triumph-03-67658406521cc.jpg', 'Avenir-Triumph-02-67658406527f3.jpg', 'Avenir-Triumph-05-6765840652a8a.jpg', 'Avenir-Triumph-01-673459868dc4e.jpg', NULL, 'Citrus Spicy', 'Avenir-Triumph-Floral-Woody-JPG-Destop-671b73c77455a.jpg', 'Avenir-Triumph-Floral-Woody-PNG-Mobil-671b73c7757ee.png', NULL, 'Euphoric burst of <br>citrus and fresh herbs', 'Avenir-Triumph-Top-Note-JPG-Destop-671b73c774b5e.jpg', 'Avenir-Triumph-Top-Note-PNG-Mobile-mi-671b73c775b96.png', NULL, 'Floral embrace elevated <br>with spices', 'Avenir-Triumph-Middle-Note-JPG-Destop-671b73c774f45.jpg', 'Avenir-Triumph-Middle-Note-PNG-Mobile-671b73c775ea9.png', NULL, 'Anchored with spicy and <br>exotic woody notes', 'Avenir-Triumph-Base-Note-JPG-Destop-671b73c7752db.jpg', 'Avenir-Triumph-Base-Note-PNG-Mobile-min-671b73c7761b0.png', 'avenir-triumph', '1', '2024-07-30 15:52:31', '2025-04-25 11:20:12', 'Memorable, Uplifting, Intense', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'AVENIR-TRIUMPH-674ff240dea8d.png', 'AVENIR-TRIUMPH-676ac5c69047f.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Morning/Daytime', 'Cruelty-free', 'Contains<br>Natural Oils', 'Contains<br>Essential Oils', NULL, 'Patchouli Oil, Lemon Oil, Jasmine Sambac, Bulgarian Rose Oil, Clove Leaf Oil.', NULL, 'Citrus Spicy', 'Avenir-Triumph-67173535e381d.png', 'Pogostemon Cablin Leaf Oil, Citrus Limon Peel, Citrus Aurantium Bergamia Fruit Oil, Orange Oil.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Avenir Triumph - Maison de l\'Avenir\'s tribute to triumph and timeless elegance.', 'Discover the triumphant aroma of Avenir Triumph, a sophisticated unisex fragrance from Maison de l\'Avenir\'s fine niche collection.', 'Avenir Triumph', 'Our AI data identifies patchouli’s earthy richness as a favorite for 65% of U.S. consumers.*', 'https://a.co/d/3xWFwcC', 'https://www.allbeauty.com/maison-de-lavenir-supernova-collection-avenir-triumph-eau-de-parfum-spray-100ml/15789708.html', '6'),
(14, 2, 'Majestic Millenium', 39.99, 'Eau De Parfum 100ml | Unisex', 'Each spritz captures the essence of adventure,  featuring the invigorating freshness of lemon,  petit grain, bitter almond, jasmine, and oud.', 'Inspired by the majestic journeys of legendary explorers, Majestic Millennium captures the essence of adventure and the thrill of uncovering new worlds. The journey begins with zesty bergamot, aromatic basil, and spicy cardamom, reminiscent of exotic spices traded along ancient routes. The invigorating freshness of lemon and petit grain mirrors the excitement of setting sail on uncharted waters. As the fragrance unfolds, a heart of timeless elegance emerges. Each spritz invites you to indulge in the refined luxury of a grand voyage, filled with the scents of far-off lands and discoveries. At its base, Majestic Millennium settles into a rich tapestry of opulent ingredients, leaving a lasting impression of sophistication and grandeur. The luxurious blend evokes the golden age of exploration, where every moment was imbued with wonder and awe.', 'Majestic-Millenium-6703e6a55ec94.png', 'Majestic-Millenium-03-676583498287e.jpg', 'Majestic-Millenium-02-6765834982dfe.jpg', 'Majestic-Millenium-05-67658349831ee.jpg', 'Majestic-Millenium-01-673459c837c64.jpg', NULL, 'Aromatic Spicy', 'Majestic-Millenium-Family-JPG-Destop-04-671b745a37985.jpg', 'Majestic-Millenium-Family-PNG-Mob-671b745a38c7f.png', NULL, 'Mighty citrus in <br>a green cape', 'Majestic-Millenium-Top-Note-JPG-Destop-03-671b745a37eeb.jpg', 'Majestic-Millenium-Top-Note-PNG-M-671b745a38fc7.png', NULL, 'Sensuously spicy with <br> a floral grandeur', 'Majestic-Millenium-Middle-Note-JPG-Destop-02-671b745a3835c.jpg', 'Majestic-Millenium-Middle-Note-PN-671b745a3932e.png', NULL, 'A legacy carved <br> in exotic wood', 'Majestic-Millenium-Base-Note-JPG-Destop-01-671b745a387a6.jpg', 'Majestic-Millenium-Base-Note-PNG-Mob-671b745a3963a.png', 'majestic-millenium', '1', '2024-07-30 15:59:28', '2025-04-25 11:19:22', 'Intriguing, Exquisite, Grandeur', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'MAJESTIC-MILLENIUM-674ff24f26d3d.png', 'MAJESTIC-MILLENIUM-6763af5b512f0.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Morning/Daytime', 'Vegan &<br>Cruelty-free', 'Contains<br>Natural Oils', 'Contains<br>Essential Oils', NULL, 'Patchouli Oil, Sandalwood Oil, Madagascar Geranium Oil, Eugenol, Lemon Oil.', NULL, 'Aromatic Spicy', 'Majestic-Millenium-67173544dd1bf.png', 'Cyperus Scariosus Root Oil, Pogostemon Cablin Oil, Pogostemon Cablin Leaf Oil, Myrtus Communis Oil.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Immerse in Timeless Luxury with Majestic Millenium by Maison de l\'Avenir', 'Elevate your senses with Majestic Millenium, a captivating unisex fragrance from Maison de l\'Avenir\'s fine niche collection.', 'Majestic Millenium', 'Our AI data identifies patchouli’s earthy richness as a favorite for 65% of U.S. consumers.*', 'https://a.co/d/5dMxNpd', 'https://www.allbeauty.com/maison-de-lavenir-supernova-collection-majestic-millenium-eau-de-parfum-spray-100ml/15789707.html', '2'),
(15, 4, 'Jardin De Jade', 29.99, 'Eau De Parfum 100ml | Unisex', 'Embrace joy as its delightful scent surrounds you  with a bouquet of lively florals-roses,  orange blossoms, heliotrope, and more.', 'Be whisked away into the world of Jardin de Jade, where every scent note is an invitation to embrace joy.  The zesty tang of bitter orange and lemon mingles with the sweet allure of cotton candy, melon, and pineapple. It\'s a fruity concoction that\'s as fun as it is refreshing, instantly lifting your spirits and putting a smile on your face. This delightful fragrance surrounds you with a bouquet of lively florals- roses, orange blossoms, heliotrope, and more. It\'s an intoxicating blend that fills you with a sense of carefree happiness and boundless optimism. And just when you think it can\'t get any better, the fragrance unfolds to reveal a rich and indulgent base of almond, sandalwood, and vanilla, adding depth and warmth to the playful concoction. It\'s like wrapping yourself in a cozy blanket of sweetness, leaving you feeling comforted, confident, and ready to take on the world.', 'Jardin-de-jadekanhiaya.png', 'Jardin-De-Jade-02-67345bbf47f04.jpg', 'Jardin-De-Jade-05-67345bbf482aa.jpg', 'Jardin-De-Jade-03-67345bbf48544.jpg', 'Jardin-De-Jade-01-67345bbf488ca.jpg', NULL, 'Fruity Floral Gourmand', 'Jardin-De-Jade-Family-JPG-Destop-04-671b7b8fd6675.jpg', 'Jardin-De-Jade-Family-PNG-Mobile-04-min-671b7b8fd75ad.png', NULL, 'A citrusy ballet <br>in floral delight', 'Jardin-De-Jade-Top-Note-JPG-Destop-03-671b7b8fd6ad7.jpg', 'Jardin-De-Jade-Top-Note-PNG-Mobile-03-min-671b7b8fd793a.png', NULL, 'Bouquet of <br>blissful elegance', 'Jardin-De-Jade-Middle-Note-JPG-Destop-02-671b7b8fd6e65.jpg', 'Jardin-De-Jade-Middle-Note-PNG-Mobile-02-min-671b7b8fd7c84.png', NULL, 'Seductive allure <br>of velvety sweetness', 'Jardin-De-Jade-Base-Note-JPG-Destop-01-671b7b8fd725e.jpg', 'Jardin-De-Jade-Base-Note-PNG-Mobile-01-mi-671b7b8fd8057.png', 'jardin-de-jade', '1', '2024-07-30 16:27:14', '2025